  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199760/extras/2be9ea18e9846e1f01a7d4080e0d8d94.webp?t=1724853375\" width=420 height=8 /></span><br>Life can change in an instant, sometimes in the wrong way. After losing someone close, a mysterious person shows up to help you get your life back together. Overcome the stages of grief in this intriguing puzzle-centric, dialogue experience and see how the story unfolds.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199760/extras/947cd9cecdd0e1707f752cc05d187ff1.webp?t=1724853375\" width=420 height=20 /></span><br>A short and sweet, solo developed indie game full of memorable conversations and simple, yet fun, puzzles.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199760/extras/9169ede6b7f0300ac6307f716c15bd19.webp?t=1724853375\" width=420 height=8 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A compelling story told through the conversations between two people.<br></li><li>50 relaxing, grid-based puzzles.<br></li><li>Different outfits to express themselves with.<br></li><li>Additional side story.<br></li><li>Soothing backgrounds and calm music.<br></li><li>Beautifully minimalistic art style.</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199760/extras/2be9ea18e9846e1f01a7d4080e0d8d94.webp?t=1724853375\" width=420 height=8 /></span><br>Life can change in an instant, sometimes in the wrong way. After losing someone close, a mysterious person shows up to help you get your life back together. Overcome the stages of grief in this intriguing puzzle-centric, dialogue experience and see how the story unfolds.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199760/extras/947cd9cecdd0e1707f752cc05d187ff1.webp?t=1724853375\" width=420 height=20 /></span><br>A short and sweet, solo developed indie game full of memorable conversations and simple, yet fun, puzzles.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2199760/extras/9169ede6b7f0300ac6307f716c15bd19.webp?t=1724853375\" width=420 height=8 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A compelling story told through the conversations between two people.<br></li><li>50 relaxing, grid-based puzzles.<br></li><li>Different outfits to express themselves with.<br></li><li>Additional side story.<br></li><li>Soothing backgrounds and calm music.<br></li><li>Beautifully minimalistic art style.</li></ul>",
